cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it presents an image segmentation approach. The use of superpixels and region growing also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The adaptive multiscale superpixel similarity and global merging strategy could also involve artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the use of boundary adherence could suggest that it belongs to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
